summary: Abeona Therapeutics ( NASDAQ:ABEO - Get Free Report ) was downgraded by StockNews.com from a "hold" rating to a "sell" rating in a research report issued on Friday. Shares of NASDAQ:ABEO opened at $4.76 on Friday. Abeona Therapeutics has a one year low of $2.19 and a one year high of $5.94.
